<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>hawbtm<ex>an</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von ein des
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der nehst vor <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        stat <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> ist <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> Niclas Griess
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, mit ew <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                        reden, und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch, was
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> zu disem mal in
                            <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>, daz ir
                        im das <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawbet. Denn wo wir ewch lieb
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>inve<ex>n</ex>c<ex>i</ex>o<ex>n</ex>is</expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>e</expan> crucis.</ab>
